      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0596P0-00838'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0596P0_19990112_GCR_107' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 27 [<span class="italic">Short title and extent</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0596P0-00839'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0596P0_19990112_GCR_108' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
