      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0596P0-00840'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0596P0_19990112_GCR_109' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 27 agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0596P0-00841'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0596P0_19990112_GCR_110' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Schedules 1 to 3 agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0596P0-00842'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0596P0_19990112_GCR_111' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Title agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0596P0-00843'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0596P0_19990112_GCR_112' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Bill reported to the House without amendment.
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0596P0-00844'>
        <a name='S5LV0596P0_19990112_GCR_113'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-geoffrey-russell' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0596P0_19990112_GCR_113' title='Link to this speech by Mr Geoffrey Russell' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-geoffrey-russell" title="Mr Geoffrey Russell">The Deputy Chairman of Committees</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            This concludes the Committee's proceedings on the Bill.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0596P0-00845'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0596P0_19990112_GCR_114' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        The Committee adjourned at twenty-eight minutes past four o'clock.
      </p>
